summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by condemnation of land and other property rights in Blocks 6 and 7, Cascade View Addition to the City of Seattle, Block 9 Cascade View Addition Division Number 2, and the south half of Tract 30 of Subdivision of Section 16, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, for open space, park and recreation purposes (Cheasty Natural Area) under the Seattle Open Space and Trails Bond Program.
